text:
This code worked before. If I push the jVisibility1 button then I want 
the "tiger" element to either get visible or hidden.
The changes are made in the dom-tree because if I reload the document 
(jSVGCanvas.setSVGDocument((SVGOMDocument)docFinal)) then it works.

void jVisibility1_actionPerformed(ActionEvent e)
  {
    final SVGOMElement visible = (SVGOMElement)docFinal.getElementById("tiger");
    if(visi1 == true)
    {
        visible.setAttribute("visibility","hidden");
        visi1 = false;
    }
    else
    {
         visible.setAttribute("visibility","visible");
         visi1 = true;
    }
    jSVGCanvas.setRenderingTransform(jSVGCanvas.getRenderingTransform());

  }
